data.name: DataPilotTableResultData
desc: information about a cell positioned within the result area of a DataPilot table.
DataPilotTableResultData contains information about a particular cell positioned within the result area of a DataPilot table.

items.name: DataFieldIndex
lines: This is a 0-based index that specifies which data field the data displayed in the cell is for; the value of 0 means the cell is for the first data field, 1 for the second, and so on.

items.name: FieldFilters
lines: This is a set of filter criteria that can be used to re-create those data rows that contribute to the value shown in the cell.

items.name: Result
lines: more information about the result contained in the DataResult type.
